    "Chen et al.",
    "45, proposed a new fusing strategy for PV power forecasting using endogenous data on an hourly scale.",
    "In their work, the DWT algorithm was employed with an adaptive neuro-fuzzy inference system (ANFIS).",
    "The decomposed PV power signal is fed into the ANFIS model for outputting short-term PV power; different functions of wavelet mother were used (Haar, Daubechies, Coiflets, and Symlets).",
